{"tid":1928035,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"世衞總幹事挑戰BTS洗手捱轟","createTime":"2020-03-16T07:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T09:10:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3beb792172bb3a4d07110b2822488cadd139623d","tid":1928035,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:04:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200316/OADQOWBFRT57UC32MB7GC6PBJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200316%2FOADQOWBFRT57UC32MB7GC6PBJA%2F&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebVI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=4ef358f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200316%2FOADQOWBFRT57UC32MB7GC6PBJA%2F&h=6bb17c14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200316/OADQOWBFRT57UC32MB7GC6PBJA/</a><br />\n<br />\n世衞總幹事挑戰BTS洗手捱轟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200316/large/1584275120_9868.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200316%2Flarge%2F1584275120_9868.jpg&h=c0489c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBTS被點名參加洗手挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐全球，要預防中招戴口罩和勤洗手最為重要，而世界衞生組織（WHO）總幹事譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）因為多次在疫情上對中國多番維護及讚美而屢受批評，未知他是否想洗底，他近日就在其個人及WHO的官方twitter上發起「THE SAFEHANDS CHALLENGE（洗手挑戰）」活動，希望大眾要關注洗手的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞更拍片親自示範如何正確洗手，同時他亦邀請韓國人氣男團防彈少年團（BTS）、美國樂壇天后Katy Perry等一同參加洗手挑戰，不過他此舉卻繼續遭到網民炮轟，指他之前遲遲不肯宣佈疫情屬大流行，令各國戒備不足，最終令武漢肺炎擴散至全球。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：施洛冰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200316/large/1584275119_46ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200316%2Flarge%2F1584275119_46ec.jpg&h=ad725ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世界衞生組織總幹事譚德塞拍片示範如何正確洗手。"},{"pid":"f6d0297b3de66df3b285b816b576543205d0db9b","tid":1928035,"uid":704,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾 屌你老母"},{"pid":"053b58a33eea4d644886ea273d213835f970f4c6","tid":1928035,"uid":196830,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPYmFcu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPYmFcu.jpg&h=66f1958a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"341559f7c96e60fa2eec7015fe1df099837a9853","tid":1928035,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"用金盤洗手啦屌你, 早走早著啦"},{"pid":"668dbac89d3eee6d12907fd0f8530c7d45a1c116","tid":1928035,"uid":21141,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"至於BTS，成員J-Hope和V上月20日曾拍片教內地粉絲如何防疫，並呼籲大家勤洗手；但BTS暫未回應譚德塞的欽點，他們的粉絲卻率先在世衛總幹事的Twitter留言大罵他腐敗，要求他辭職，聲稱在疫症爆發初期，讓韓國人冒性命危險，指他在當地聲譽很差，別利用BTS達到政治目的<br />\n<br />\n人地上個月就叫人做，依家先來馬後炮仲想借啲意掀起名人效應，會唔會太㭍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b54563ca8fb3603d5a417fc07ee31c6b809761","tid":1928035,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"一月頭post就話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee5fc1c11b28efb626c7cb9da2342d4fce75dec","tid":1928035,"uid":16459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f319ecb605a12ec56189e67b6c333aff67641e","tid":1928035,"uid":155902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\